<Layout title="About Page">
	<main>
	  <section class="about-section">
		<div class="container">
		  <div class="about-content">
			<div class="team-story">
			  <h2>Our Story</h2>
			  <p>
				FinEdge was born with a single objective, of enabling wealth creation for our clients through quality and conflict-free investment management. The use of technology is our cornerstone in ensuring that we can reach across demographics and geographies, provide a convenient, low-cost - high-quality, process-driven, goal-oriented, wealth creation platform.
			  </p>
			  <p>
				We are experts at what we do and for us, our success lies only in making our clients meet their investment objectives. We love the fact that we are known and respected by our clients and the industry for our unique business model and our conflict-free advice.
			  </p>
			</div>
		  </div>
  
		  <div class="about-content">
			<img src="https://www.finedge.in/assets/uploads/files/ed224-img-1.jpg" alt="About Image" class="about-image">
			<div class="about-person">
			  <h2>Harsh Gahlaut<br /><span>Co-Founder & CEO</span></h2>
			  <p>
				Harsh co-founded FinEdge after successfully managing several large businesses in the Financial Services Industry. He is a Management Graduate with over 21 years of experience in institutions like Xerox, Standard Chartered Bank, Dawnay Day AV, and Religare Macquarie.
			  </p>
			  <a target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/harsh-gahlaut-6658068/"><i></i></a>
			</div>
		  </div>
  
		  <div class="about-content">
			<img src="https://www.finedge.in/assets/uploads/files/e34a2-mayank-photo.jpg" alt="About Image" class="about-image">
			<div class="about-person">
			  <h2>Mayank Bhatnagar<br /><span>Co-Founder & COO</span></h2>
			  <p>
				Mayank co-founded FinEdge and has a professional experience of more than 20 years across retail and corporate banking. His expertise in global transaction banking and retail assets in Standard Chartered Bank has been critical in setting up the FinEdge business intelligence platform.
			  </p>
			  <a target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mayank-bhatnagar-b6488b8/"><i></i></a>
			</div>
		  </div>
  
		  <div class="about-content">
			<img src="https://www.finedge.in/assets/uploads/files/b6fea-img-4.jpg" alt="About Image" class="about-image">
			<div class="about-person">
			  <h2>Aniruddha Bose<br /><span>Chief Business Officer</span></h2>
			  <p>
				Aniruddha holds an MBA with Distinction from Sa√Ød Business School, University of Oxford. He has 16 years of experience in the Investment Advisory space with institutions like Destimoney & Standard Chartered Bank. Aniruddha is a founding team member and has been instrumental in setting up and leading key business processes, strategies, and systems for FinEdge.
			  </p>
			  <a target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/aniruddha-bose-8375b75/"><i></i></a>
			</div>
		  </div>
  
		  <div class="about-content">
			<img src="https://www.finedge.in/assets/uploads/files/84269-gaurav-photo.jpg" alt="About Image" class="about-image">
			<div class="about-person">
			  <h2>Gaurav Agarwal<br /><span>Co-Founder</span></h2>
			  <p>
				Gaurav is a management graduate with a major in marketing and strategy. With over 15 years of work experience, Gaurav has set up multiple e-commerce companies and successfully managed large distribution businesses for ITC and Nokia.
			  </p>
			  <a target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/gaurav-agarwal-7a0863b1/"><i></i></a>
			</div>
		  </div>
		</div>
	  </section>
	</main>
  </Layout>
  
  <style>
	.about-section {
	  padding: 50px 0;
	  background-color: #f4f4f4;
	}
  
	.container {
	  max-width: 1200px;
	  margin: 0 auto;
	  padding: 0 20px;
	}
  
	.about-content {
	  display: flex;
	  align-items: center;
	  margin-bottom: 35px;
	}

	.about-person {
	  width: 100%;
	  background-color: #ffffff;
	  border: 1px solid #6b21a8;
	  padding: 20px;
	  margin-left: 60px;
	  text-align: center;

	}
  
	.about-person h2 {
	  margin: 0;
	  color: #6b21a8;
	  font-size: 20px;
	  line-height: 1.3;
	}
  
	.about-person span {
	  display: block;
	  color: #888;
	  font-size: 14px;
	}
  
	.about-person p {
	  color: #333;
	  margin-top: 15px;
	}
  
	.about-person a {
	  display: inline-block;
	  margin-top: 10px;
	}
  </style>
